Recycle candy wrappers, chip bags, or card wrappers into a cute zippered pouch. It even has a loop so you can wear it around your wrist. This step-by-step tutorial will show you how to put a zipper in your recycled wrapper pouch. Easy project for beginning sewers!

For written instructions visit: http://www.madebymarzipan.com/?p=4647 

